{
  "texts": [
    "u att is described in Section \"Attention-based User Interest Extraction\".",
    "To estimate the probability that a user will click on a candidate news item, we implement and evaluate two representative approaches for click prediction, drawing inspiration from the NAML (An et al. 2019) and DKN (Wang et al. 2018) models.",
    "Dot Product-Based Predictor.",
    "Following the approach proposed in NAML and earlier work by (Okura et al. 2017), we use the dot product between the user representation u and the candidate news representation r c to compute the click probability:",
    "Neural Network-Based Predictor."
  ]
}